jobs.description:
**Entity:** Oracle America, Inc.  



**Job Duties** : Design, develop, troubleshoot and/or test/QA software. As a member of the software engineering division, apply knowledge of software architecture to perform tasks associated with developing, debugging, or designing software applications or operating systems according to provided design specifications. Build enhancements within an existing software architecture and/or suggest improvements to the architecture. May telecommute. (385\.29993\)  



Employer will accept a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Engineering or related technical field and 1 year of experience in the job offered or in a Software Developer\-related occupation.  



Position Requires:


* Writing backend code using Java, Python, C\+\+, or similar OO language and front\-end code using either of AngularJS, ReactJS, Typescript;
* Cloud Infrastructure and Automation operating in a major cloud provider including OCI, AWS, Azure, or GCP;
* MacOS and Apple Hardware having strong knowledge in bare metal provision, automated OS deployments;
* Microservice, REST API Development and understanding of databases including MySQL, Oracle, MongoDB, MS SQL Server, SQL, or PL/SQL;
* Monitoring, Observability, logging with tools including Graphana , Prometheus with mission\-critical services;
* LINUX \& Networking fundamentals; and
* Devops principals including CI/CD, Kubernetes and Infrastructure as Code (IAC) languages including Terraform.
